{
  "stem": "7506.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I couldn't walk down the streets where my aunts and uncles had lived, where my grandparents had lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I just-- I wanted to be a million miles away from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[SIGH] I went to England, first alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Back to my great-grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And the family, as such, when they started getting demobilized out of the British forces-- my uncles, my two uncles, my mother's eldest brother, my mother's youngest brother, and other uncles.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, they have me on their hands, 14 years old, very combative.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Don't tell me what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Where I've been, you wouldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You wouldn't dream of where I've been.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You either go to school, or you work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to work, you must learn to do something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you don't want to go to school to study, you must learn to do something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my mother's eldest brother, and indeed, her youngest brothers, had been beauticians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES] So my uncle, the oldest one, Sam, said to me, do you want to learn my business?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES] So I said, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't want to do nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't want to learn nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES] So I was apprenticed to learn that business [PAUSES] in England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But because of my differences with my uncle and my differences with my mother's aunt, Auntie [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ray, ?] because nobody told me anything, I went to live with another uncle [PAUSES] in another part of London.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By that time, my mother had left Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So had my aunt [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anne. ?] So had my cousin, of course, and had come to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
